_text = "Is it bad I want to get lost out here? I want the trees to swallow me whole, and keep me locked away inside the safety of their branches.\n\nOut here I feel like i’m truly at my happiests. All year I count the days until I can go camping. Its winter at the time I’m creating this, and I can’t help but feel snowed in. Trapped in this log cabin, waiting for the frost to thaw. Waiting for something to grab and pull me in.\n\nSometimes I fear my craving for adventure is too much for my 9 to 5 responsibilities. Is it naive to drop everything and live in the woods?"

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, BirbMemory, BirbMemory, false)
